ntime system properties for io.vertx:vertx-web-client:5.0.1 as well: -Dsun.misc.unsafe.memory.access=allow and -Dio.netty.tryReflectionSetAccessible=true. Use an in-process Vert.x HttpServer on 127.0.0.1 with an ephemeral port for WebClient coverage rather than external network services.\",\n  \"risks\": [\n    \"The public OAuth2WebClient API references io.vertx:vertx-auth-oauth2, which is optional and not pulled transitively; avoid OAuth2-specific tests unless intentionally adding that optional dependency.\",\n    \"External live HTTP services would make tests flaky and are unnecessary because the client can be exercised against an embedded Vert.x server.\"\n  ]\n}", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_071cb6a134bb791d016a411fb7a1bc81948083993166c4f585\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 938, "output": 1078, "cacheRead": 33792, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 35808, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1782652844816, "responseId": "resp_071cb6a134bb791d016a411fad659c819490754188c912b0ae"}}
